.main-head
	.container
		.row
			.col-sm-12
				h1.brand.text-center 
					a(href="/")
						img.logo(src="/app/img/post-parcel-logo.png", alt="Post & Parcel")
		.row.description
			.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1
				p.hook <em>With no account neccessary, Post &amp; Parcel allows you to creat HTML newsletters by letting you pick bits and pieces of already made templates while choosing your own content. You may send emails to your entire mailing by using SendGrid's marketing email system with no cost to you.</em>
		.row.template-cta
			.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-4
				button.btn.send-btn-alt(ng-click="moveTop()") Pick Your Template

.container
	.row(ng-controller="MainCtrl")
		.col-lg-4.col-sm-6.front.text-center(ng-repeat="thumbnail in templates")
			img.template-thumbnail(ng-src="{{thumbnail.img}}", alt="{{thumbnail.alt}}")
			.highlighted.back
				.thumbnail-name
					h2 {{thumbnail.name}}
				.thumbnail-cta
					a.btn.send-btn-alt(href="{{thumbnail.url}}", ng-click="openView(thumbnail.sref)") Use Template

footer.footer(ng-include="'/partials/main/footer'")